          {
            "nodeType": "paragraph",
            "data": {},
            "content": [
              {
                "nodeType": "text",
                "value": "Movement uses square-grid counting where edge-to-edge and corner-to-corner each cost 1 space. Major movement generally risks opportunity actions; minor movement does not.",
